name: Coreicon Pro v01.3 (preview)
description:
Coreicon Pro includes 250 UI icons for web, iOS, Android, and desktop apps synced with Awwwards, MIT licensed, and built in Ukraine.


Features

📐 Based on 24px grid

💡 100% Customizable

🔐 MIT Licence

🧬 Component Library

💎 Pixel perfect

🧩 Figma, IconJar, .SVG


After payment we deliver:

  • Figma library (where all icons are stroke and vectors);
  • IconJar package;
  • Archive folder with 250.SVG icons.


Support

Have questions? Let's talk or add a request to support@coreicon.dev
